-- Seven shares on trading halt ahead of announcement
-- 
-- Sun Nov 19, 2006 11:24pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/11/20/us-media-australia-seven-halt-idUSSYU00113120061120

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Shares in Australia's Seven Network Ltd. SEV.AX have been placed on a trading halt pending the release of an announcement from the company. 

 The Australian Financial Review reported on Monday that Seven was in talks with private equity group Kohlberg Kravis Roberts on a A$3.5 billion ($2.7 billion) deal to go private.